  "subject": "Remove hardcoded cloudRegionId, Pass flavor dict",
  "commit_message": "Remove hardcoded cloudRegionId, Pass flavor dict\n\nThis change removes hardcoded RegionOne cloud\nregion from homing flavor code. Until this patch,\nSO homing passed <cloud-region-name>_flavorList to\nsub BPMN flows to pass along flavor label\ninformation. Now flavorLists are passed as a\ndict, allowing consuming BPMN flows\nto access a generic dict containing flavor info\ninstead of a hardcoded RegionOne_flavorList.\n\nIssue-ID: SO-671\nChange-Id: Id6ab524fb18344b3a76f873b71171ccde8adb5d2\nSigned-off-by: Marcus G K Williams <marcus.williams@intel.com>\n",
